text: Herbertsville is an unincorporated community located within Brick Township in Ocean County, New Jersey, United States.Locality Search, State of New Jersey. Accessed March 14, 2015. The suburban community is located in the northern reaches of the township centered about the intersection of Herbertsville Road (County Route 549 Spur) and Lanes Mill Road. ==References== Category:Brick Township, New Jersey Category:Unincorporated communities in Ocean County, New Jersey Category:Unincorporated communities in New Jersey
